race.comment: KEITEL (2) hasn't done much wrong since joining the Vandyke yard with a win and two placings from three starts and should be cherry-ripe now fourth run in. Has placed over this mile journey and should be hitting the line with gusto. FREE CARRY (4) goes well for jockey Lang who has four wins and three placings from ten rides. Is a four-time winner over this trip and is sure to prove very hard to hold out. LUDOVISI (8) has two wins and two placings from just five attempts at the trip and gets in well at the weights with the claim. Top-three contender. EXCEED SPEED (6) has a win and a second from three spins around this circuit and may trouble the judge with any luck in running. CUNNAMULLA FELLA (1) best of the rest in a competitive affair to close out the card.
